    "However, feature extraction via the DT algorithm is often subject to environmental constraints.",
    "For this reason, Wang et al. (2013) proposed an improved dense trajectory (IDT) method in 2013.",
    "This is a more advanced video feature extraction method.",
    "The IDT descriptor shows how spatial and temporal signals can be processed differently.",
    "Instead of extending the Harris corner detector to 3D, it starts with densely sampled feature points in the video frame and uses the optical flow to track them."
  ],
